---

## Decisions Made

1. Implement "Vet Mode" with destination obscuring
2. Scenic route option (max 10 min overhead by default)
3. Treat budget auto-boost to 20 for vet rides
4. Owner can force-book without dog confirmation
5. Track vet-specific anxiety metrics over time

## Results (Post-Implementation)

After 2 weeks of Vet Mode:

| Metric | Before | After |
|--------|--------|-------|
| Vet ride completion | 34% | 67% |
| Avg vet ride wag score | 2.1 | 4.8 |
| Owner satisfaction (vet rides) | 2.3/5 | 4.1/5 |

Dogs are still reluctant, but the experience is much better.
